Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But the only one in here with a boyfriend is Takanashi, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it going with Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The bond between the Wicked Eye and Dark Flame Master is unshakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means... normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So no trouble but no progress either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to talk about Master and Dark Flame Master until my death?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what else are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you want to tell us there's someone {\i1}you{\i0} like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.09,0:00:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud: someone you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So someone worthy of forming a contract with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A servant with such a huge amount of dark power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not listening at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A contract can only be made with a compatible being.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it differently, to find one is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, actually finding one yourself {\i1}is{\i0} pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have a worthy woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You? You really have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing that comes to mind is her being huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just because you're tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other personal data?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A delinquent!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling us she even surpasses the Dark Flame Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.86,0:01:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make them fight to death sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something you decide without those two being around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's dark-skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A sportsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But most importantly, she can breathe fire of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A street performer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the death is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Níðhöggr!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the black dragon of death who survived Ragnarök.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:01:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a lizard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a lizard, she's the dragon of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Same difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nibutani, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lizards resemble salamanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas dragons are a completely different species.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Salamanders are–
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you like about little Níðhöggr, Deko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She has the highest attack power of all familiars I control.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to always be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of time to listen to you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think of something too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, you have little Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chimera! My dear familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how stupid was I to expect her to behave like a normal girl?
